  <summary date="2025-09-26T15:22:53Z" status="Introduced in House">This bill repeals the Impoundment Control Act of 1974 (ICA).&#160;The&#160;ICA generally limits the authority of the President to impound (i.e., withhold from obligation or expenditure) funds that have been appropriated by Congress and establishes related procedures. It&#160;also establishes expedited legislative procedures that Congress may use to consider legislation to enact rescissions proposed by the President.&#160;</summary>
